reviewText: I basically liked these shorts.  A couple were quite good, but one prompted me to fast forward.  There are other, better collections of short, gay-themed films.
summary: I liked this more than some,  less than others

reviewText: Everything is said in my heading.  This was one of the WORST downloads I have had from Amazon.  The quality was grainey, the sound was out of sync and garbuled.  Wasn't worth 5 cents,  yet I was stupid enough to have spent 3 bucks on it..
